'''RingCube vDesk''' is a [[Desktop virtualization]] product from RingCube Technologies. vDesk is a client virtualization or virtual workspace platform which virtualizes the entire desktop at an operating system level. The platform can be deployed in four different modes: on a local PC, on an external USB device, streamed across a network, or in conjunction with existing [[VDI]] solutions.<ref>http://www.networkworld.com/columnists/2008/091108-gearhead.html</ref>
